point (if \eqn{s < 0}), or less than the lower end point (if \eqn{s > 0}).

The parametric form of the GEV encompasses that of the Gumbel, Frechet and
reverse Weibull distributions, which are obtained for \eqn{s = 0}, \eqn{s >
